{"tid":1108635,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五項措施便利本港電影業內地發展","createTime":"2019-04-16T05:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T07:44:40.000Z","uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d577b754bccf8ccf785aa8d44f20f34c63167e74","tid":1108635,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:39:51.000Z","msg":"個個明星上去揾真錢 全港都睇鳳凰衛視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭：中央同意5項措施便利本港電影業內地發展<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥出席行政會議前宣布，中央政府原則上同意實行5項便利本港電影業界進入內地市場的措施，<span style=\"color: red;\">包括不限港人參與內地製作的數目、不限兩地合拍片演員及內地元素比例、取消收取香港及內地合拍片立項申報費用、香港電影及電影人可報名參評內地獎項</span>、香港電影企業在港澳地區及海外發行推廣優秀內地電影和合拍片可申請奬勵。但放寬香港電影在內地發行則仍在商討。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，商務及經濟發展局會跟進有關實行細節，希望盡快落實，她又提到，相信中央短期會有其他措施，<span style=\"color: red;\">讓香港人在內地參與更多內地影視，享有更多發展機遇及交流空間，</span>政府樂意為業界開拓更多與內地溝通的渠道。"},{"pid":"004374d7002a60b26bdf274af37f09a724c534d4","tid":1108635,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87ef1408c1c5e500725f26eb71ab196ef65ee47","tid":1108635,"uid":224565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"咪又係比中共斂財<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8409abc4c70b55786921f4f6c01398747551d65c","tid":1108635,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d87ef1408c1c5e500725f26eb71ab196ef65ee47","tid":1108635,"uid":224565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"咪又係比中共斂財<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" cla